 FOSHAN MOTORCYCLE CO.,LTD.|website=www.cccme.org.cn}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Znen]] || China || Zhongneng Vehicle Group Co., Ltd.; petrol and electric scooters. Sold under numerous brands including Jinlun (worldwide), Lexmoto (UK), Tamoretti (UK, Netherlands), Dorton (Spain), Mondial (Turkey), and in the USA Paparazzi's, Flyscooters, Lance, and BMS. Owners of Moto Morini. \n|-\n| Zunlong || China || Manufactured by Benzhou Vehicle Industry Group Co., Ltd. and Taizhou Huangyan Yiying Motorcycle Co., Ltd.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://auto-che.com/b/zunlong.html|title=Zunlong Made In China|website=auto-che.com}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Z Electric Vehicle]] || USA || All electric range\n|}\n\n==Scooter brands and manufacturers no longer in scooter production==\n*Accumolli (1950), [[Piaggio]] powered  &mdash; Italy<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.woiweb.com/wiki/index.php?title=Accumolli|title=Accumolli - WOI Encyclopedia Italia|website=www.woiweb.com}}</ref>\n*Achilles (1953\u20141957) &mdash; West Germany<ref name=\"auto\">{{cite web|url=https://cybermotorcycle.com/euro/germany.htm|title=German Motorcycles|website=Classic Motorcycles at Sheldon's Emu}}</ref>\n*[[ACMA (Ateliers de construction de motocycles et d'automobiles) |ACMA (Vespa)]] (1951\u20141962), Ateliers de Construction de Motocycles et Accessoires &mdash; France<ref name=\"auto2\">{{cite web|url=https://cybermotorcycle.com/euro/france.htm|title=French Motorcycles|website=Classic Motorcycles at Sheldon's Emu}}</ref>\n*Adonis (1949\u20141952), Soci\u00e9t\u00e9 du Scooters Adonis; 50 and 75cc VAP engines &mdash; France<ref name=\"auto3\">{{Cite web|url=https://cybermotorcycle.com/euro/france.htm|title=French Motorcycles|website=Classic Motorcycles at Sheldon's Emu}}</ref>\n*Aermoto (1938\u20141940), [[Sachs Motorcycles |Sachs]] powered  &mdash; Italy<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.woiweb.com/wiki/index.php?title=Aermoto|title=Aermoto - WOI Encyclopedia Italia|website=www.woiweb.com}}</ref>\n*[[Agrati]] (1958\u20141965), Merged wi