7.ghtml|title=Santa Catarina confirma 57 casos.|website=G1|date=21 March 2020}}</ref>\n! 459 <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://g1.globo.com/sp/sao-paulo/noticia/2020/03/21/numero-de-mortes-por-coronavirus-em-sp-sobe-para-15-segundo-governo-do-estado.ghtml|title=S\u00e3o Paulo tem 459 casos confirmados.|last=|first=|date=21 March 2020|website=G1|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n! 16 <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://g1.globo.com/ms/mato-grosso-do-sul/noticia/2020/03/21/mato-grosso-do-sul-tem-16-casos-de-coronavirus-e-estado-comeca-liberar-hr-para-pacientes-com-a-doenca.ghtml|title=Mato Grosso do Sul confirma 16 casos.|website=G1|date=21 March 2020}}</ref>\n! 10 <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://g1.globo.com/se/sergipe/noticia/2020/03/21/sobe-para-10-o-numero-de-pessoas-infectadas-pelo-novo-coronavirus-em-sergipe.ghtml|title=Sergipe confirma 10 casos.|website=G1|date=21 March 2020}}</ref>\n! 11 <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://g1.globo.com/ac/acre/noticia/2020/03/21/secretaria-de-saude-do-acre-registra-11-casos-de-covid-19.ghtml|title=Acre confirma 11 casos.|website=G1|date=21 March 2020}}</ref>\n! 3 <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://g1.globo.com/ro/rondonia/noticia/2020/03/21/rondonia-confirma-mais-2-casos-de-coronavirus-total-vai-a-3.ghtml|title=Rond\u00f4nia confirma 3 casos.|website=G1|date=21 March 2020}}</ref>\n! 2 <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://g1.globo.com/pa/para/noticia/2020/03/20/sespa-confirma-segundo-caso-de-covid-19-no-para.ghtml|title=Par\u00e1 confirma 2 casos.|website=G1|date=20 March 2020}}</ref>\n! 2 <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://g1.globo.com/rr/roraima/noticia/2020/03/21/governo-confirma-dois-primeiros-casos-de-coronavirus-em-rr.ghtml|title=Roraima confirma 2 casos.|website=G1|date=21 March 2020}}</ref>\n! 1 <ref>{[Cite web|url=https://g1.globo.com/ap/amapa/noticia/2020/03/20/coronavirus-amapa-tem-1-caso-confirmado-e-monitora-39-suspeitos-em-4-municipios.ghtml|title=Amap\u00e1<nowiki> confirma 1 caso.|website=G1|date=20 March 2020}}</nowiki></ref>\n!